            {
              "enText": "<b>Lesson 12 • Running a meeting</b>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "Julia is running a meeting. When Larry and Sally start arguing, Julia has to bring the meeting back under control."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Julia:</b> Let's <b>get down to business</b>. We need to <b>cover a lot of ground</b>. Our first <b>agenda item</b> is to figure out how we're going to respond to all the complaints we've been getting about our new website."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Larry:</b> Just so we're all <b>on the same page</b>, please give us an overview of the problem."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Julia:</b> <b>In a nutshell</b>, our customers are complaining that it's very difficult to place orders through the new website."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Sally:</b> I think we <b>jumped the gun</b> by not conducting focus groups with our customers before we launched our new website."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Larry:</b> More focus groups? <b>Every time I turn around</b> we're running focus groups! It's <b>gotten out of hand</b>."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Sally:</b> <b>I beg to differ</b>. Focus groups are very important. They help us better understand our customer."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Julia:</b> Well, clearly you two <b>don't see eye-to-eye</b> on this issue."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Larry:</b> Ha! <b>That's putting it lightly</b>! Focus groups are a waste of time and…..."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Julia:</b> Excuse me, let's not <b>get off track</b> here. Does anybody else want to <b>weigh in on the issue at hand</b>?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Carl:</b> If I can <b>put in my two cents</b>, I agree with Sally that focus groups would've been a good idea."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Julia:</b> Well, enough about focus groups for now. Let's move on to our next agenda item — planning for our <b>company offsite</b>."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Larry:</b> Wait, I'm not finished talking about the website!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Julia:</b> We can <b>circle back</b> to that at the end of our meeting if we have time. I want to keep us on schedule since I know many of us have another meeting at 11 o'clock."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
